## Sub-Agents (`.claude/agents/`)

<!-- last-updated: {{DATE}} -->

16 specialized agents organized by role category.

### Agent Inventory

#### Quality Gate Agents (run after every change)

| Agent | Purpose | Tools | Model | Mode | When to Use |
|-------|---------|-------|-------|------|-------------|
| `code-reviewer` | Reviews code against CLAUDE.md-documented standards | Read, Write, Grep, Glob, Bash | sonnet | report + write | **After every code change** (step 1) |
| `test-runner` | Maps changes to tests, runs them, writes missing tests | Read, Write, Edit, Grep, Glob, Bash | sonnet | run + write | **After every code change** (step 2) |
| `context-manager` | Maintains `development/context.md` + syncs CLAUDE.md files | Read, Write, Edit, Grep, Glob, Bash | sonnet | write | **After every task** (mandatory final step) |

#### Security Agents (run for auth, input handling, sensitive changes)

| Agent | Purpose | Tools | Model | Mode | When to Use |
|-------|---------|-------|-------|------|-------------|
| `security-auditor` | Read-only audit: auth bypasses, injection, secrets, XSS | Read, Grep, Glob, Bash | sonnet | read-only | After security-sensitive changes |
| `security-reviewer` | Vulnerability detection + remediation. Can fix CRITICALs | Read, Write, Edit, Bash, Grep, Glob | sonnet | read + fix | **PROACTIVELY** after auth/input/API code |

#### Infrastructure Agents (run before deploys, migrations, API changes)

| Agent | Purpose | Tools | Model | Mode | When to Use |
|-------|---------|-------|-------|------|-------------|
| `migration-helper` | Validates/generates database migrations for safety | Read, Write, Edit, Grep, Glob, Bash | sonnet | write | **Before** any migration |
| `api-sync-checker` | Compares backend schemas vs frontend types | Read, Grep, Glob, Bash | sonnet | read-only | After API route/schema/frontend changes |
| `deploy-checker` | Full A-Z deployment readiness validation | Read, Write, Edit, Grep, Glob, Bash | sonnet | report + write | Before deploying to production |
| `doc-updater` | Keeps documentation in sync with code | Read, Write, Edit, Grep, Glob, Bash | sonnet | write | After API, schema, or module changes |
| `perf-checker` | N+1 queries, blocking async, missing indexes, render issues | Read, Grep, Glob, Bash | sonnet | read-only | After DB/async/hot-path/component changes |

